  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889040/extras/755c8e973264c7b1d522901f35020c83.avif?t=1739362118\" width=587 height=125 /></span><br><br>Birth is an adventure game about constructing a creature from spare bones & organs found around the city in order to quell your loneliness. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect bones & organs in hand-drawn museums, coffee shops, alleys, flower shops, libraries, markets, bakeries and more.<br></li><li>Solve physics-based puzzles & interact with unique, interesting creatures.<br></li><li>Find & spend hidden tokens to discover secrets.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889040/extras/d31210ddf39b0006ab0871da212b4313.poster.avif?t=1739362118\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889040/extras/d31210ddf39b0006ab0871da212b4313.webm?t=1739362118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889040/extras/d31210ddf39b0006ab0871da212b4313.mp4?t=1739362118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889040/extras/755c8e973264c7b1d522901f35020c83.avif?t=1739362118\" width=587 height=125 /></span><br><br>Birth is an adventure game about constructing a creature from spare bones & organs found around the city in order to quell your loneliness. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect bones & organs in hand-drawn museums, coffee shops, alleys, flower shops, libraries, markets, bakeries and more.<br></li><li>Solve physics-based puzzles & interact with unique, interesting creatures.<br></li><li>Find & spend hidden tokens to discover secrets.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889040/extras/d31210ddf39b0006ab0871da212b4313.poster.avif?t=1739362118\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889040/extras/d31210ddf39b0006ab0871da212b4313.webm?t=1739362118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889040/extras/d31210ddf39b0006ab0871da212b4313.mp4?t=1739362118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
